node.text:
Father, please help them……. 😭 
And please let everyone that supported Joe and Kamala, in any way, via raising funds, pushing their narrative, or outright lying for them, become sick to their stomachs as they see what this administration has done… let America never again be taken over by evil, senile, tyrant elites like we have now, let America long for good and just leadership to represent us. Let us all wake up from our slumber, shake off the chains of apathy, and stand once again in unity asking you, Creator of the Universe, Father of Light, Author of Justice, Truth and Love, to take your rightful place in our hearts. Not second chair, not on the shelf, but first place in our lives… Let us look to You Now, Seek You like never before, let us stop playing church, and actually become the bride that you desire… Let us come to you with our whole heart, mind, soul and strength… For you, alone oh God, are our salvation… You are our hope, you are our joy… and only You, deserve our praise… Pull us together Father, let this unify your children, I ask, in the beautiful name of our Big Brother Yeshua…….. ❤️🙏🏽❤️
Amen
